dex, or opencode, because it's pty-pane-level injection, not an API the host has to expose. Layered on top: LLM-distilled activity broadcast means OTHER agents can see "what X is doing right now" without polling or reading X's transcript — awareness as a first-class wire concept (`Status.activity`, kind:30315), not just presence. \n
